title: Default values are not shown in 'Show Report Parameters' dialog
description: When creating several report parameters and setting default values for them, the default values are not displayed in the 'Show Report Parameters' dialog. To reproduce the issue, follow the steps below:
OB:
1. Create several report parameters.
2. Set default values for the report parameters.
3. Drag them to the Layout.
EB: The default values should be displayed in the 'Show Report Parameters' dialog after dragging the report parameters to the layout.
SR: Fix the issue so that the default values of the report parameters are correctly shown in the 'Show Report Parameters' dialog.
